INFORMATION:-

Two separated half siblings meet for the first time. The 27-year-old Charlotte leads a comfortable life as a dance teacher for children and she has a relationship with the brother of her best friend. She meets her half brother Henrik for the first time after it has been moved to Oslo. The result is a brother-zusrelatie between two people who have never known a normal family environment. The relationship evolves to throw themselves into a self-destructive sexual attraction that threatens their lives upside down.
